data.description: This completely renovated gem is guaranteed to impress.   With 4 spacious bedrooms plus a den/office and 2 full bathrooms, this home has all the modern features you are looking for.    Situated on a huge and private corner lot, with ample room for a pool and large outdoor entertainment areas, this is a rare find in the desirable community of Vizcaya in Miramar.     Conveniently located to major highways and nearby shopping and amenities, yet in a peaceful serene neighborhood, the home provides the perfect balance between city life and suburban privacy and tranquility.
